com.sap.spe.condmgnt.finding

Interface ITracerAttributeMap


  • public interface ITracerAttributeMap
    Interface of the tracerAttributeMap-object. This object stores information about the mapping between conditionTable-keyfields and document attributes. A list of the tracerAttributeMap-objects is stored by the tracerAccess.
